WEBVTT

00:01:08.465 --> 00:01:10.545
Our livelihood is more important.

00:01:10.625 --> 00:01:11.705
I should not get soft, right?

00:01:11.785 --> 00:01:14.585
The tutoring school project
that's going to be at Play Park's location

00:01:14.665 --> 00:01:16.865
is a chance to prove my capability.

00:01:16.945 --> 00:01:20.425
I'm sorry for not being able
to keep Play Park running.

00:01:20.505 --> 00:01:21.865
I understand you as well.

00:01:21.945 --> 00:01:23.825
Everyone has their own needs.

00:01:24.625 --> 00:01:27.425
If your family were still together,

00:01:27.505 --> 00:01:28.905
I would have stepped away.

00:01:28.985 --> 00:01:31.265
I… I need to leave.

00:01:32.945 --> 00:01:35.585
So it's not just me, right?

00:02:14.585 --> 00:02:15.505
Ms. Lin.

00:02:31.225 --> 00:02:33.265
Waiting for your handsome date?

00:02:34.185 --> 00:02:35.425
He won't show up.

00:02:36.665 --> 00:02:39.905
Ms. Lin is going on a date.
Ms. Lin is going on a date.

00:02:41.625 --> 00:02:42.665
Going on a date…

00:02:50.585 --> 00:02:53.985
Oh, Ms. Manager. What are you doing here?

00:02:54.585 --> 00:02:57.025
What about you, Ms. secretary?
What brings you here?

00:02:58.665 --> 00:03:00.225
Well…

00:03:00.305 --> 00:03:03.025
Well, if Ms. Lin found out

00:03:03.105 --> 00:03:08.265
that her secretary was working with a man
to set up a date, how would she feel?

00:03:10.385 --> 00:03:14.625
Though, to stop me from telling your boss,

00:03:15.305 --> 00:03:17.185
it's actually really easy.

00:03:18.025 --> 00:03:21.145
How would you like me to help?
Please tell me, Ms. Manager.

00:03:22.705 --> 00:03:24.905
Cancel that dinner date,

00:03:24.985 --> 00:03:28.465
and this will remain
a secret forever, okay?

00:03:32.425 --> 00:03:36.905
Please don't tell Ms. Jane off.
I promised her.

00:03:36.985 --> 00:03:40.945
I won't. She did it
because she cares about me.

00:03:43.545 --> 00:03:47.345
And why didn't you seem surprised
when you saw me here?

00:03:47.425 --> 00:03:51.305
Because someone was tailing me
everywhere at Play Park.

00:03:51.865 --> 00:03:52.985
It's not hard to guess.

00:03:54.625 --> 00:03:55.985
When did you spot me?

00:03:58.145 --> 00:04:00.225
You bought me a drink today,

00:04:00.305 --> 00:04:03.265
so let me treat you to dinner.

00:04:03.865 --> 00:04:05.465
Gladly.

00:04:08.785 --> 00:04:11.785
The waiter at the cafe
was also your spy, right?

00:04:13.065 --> 00:04:14.345
Ms. Lin.

00:04:14.945 --> 00:04:18.785
Did you intentionally mention
this place's name so I could follow you?

00:04:19.665 --> 00:04:22.025
It's because your jealousy was obvious.

00:04:23.505 --> 00:04:25.505
You're so cunning.

00:04:26.465 --> 00:04:30.145
If you have something on your mind,
just tell me.

00:04:30.225 --> 00:04:33.065
Do I seem like an unreasonable person?

00:04:35.585 --> 00:04:37.065
I'm sorry.

00:04:54.945 --> 00:04:57.185
Should we go somewhere else?

00:05:28.665 --> 00:05:32.465
Honestly,
I should thank that handsome guy.

00:05:33.865 --> 00:05:36.665
For making you realize you're jealous?

00:05:39.345 --> 00:05:43.105
I just don't like it
when someone gets close to you.

00:05:43.185 --> 00:05:45.945
Men and women.

00:05:49.145 --> 00:05:51.705
Can I ask why you rushed home that day?

00:06:02.785 --> 00:06:04.505
I need to leave.

00:06:07.145 --> 00:06:09.185
Can we not talk about this?

00:06:09.945 --> 00:06:13.305
If it still lingers in my mind,
I can't move on.

00:06:14.345 --> 00:06:15.785
No, I won't talk about it.

00:06:17.225 --> 00:06:20.025
-We'll make it short.
-No.

00:06:20.105 --> 00:06:21.585
Just a bit.

00:06:23.625 --> 00:06:24.985
Well…

00:06:26.825 --> 00:06:29.745
I've never been in a relationship
with a woman.

00:06:32.905 --> 00:06:34.945
I'm new to this as well.

00:06:35.025 --> 00:06:38.705
You? I don't believe it.

00:06:40.225 --> 00:06:45.225
I was worried too.
I've been watching those shows a little.

00:06:45.305 --> 00:06:47.505
So I was trying to do what they do.

00:06:49.905 --> 00:06:52.145
That's why it felt familiar.

00:06:55.945 --> 00:06:59.665
So, we're dating now, right?

00:07:01.825 --> 00:07:02.825
I don't know.

00:07:07.505 --> 00:07:09.145
Be serious.

00:07:11.945 --> 00:07:13.025
Yes, I guess.

00:07:27.945 --> 00:07:29.625
I can't breathe.

00:07:33.905 --> 00:07:37.905
Let's remember it.
Today's the first day of our relationship.

00:07:39.265 --> 00:07:40.465
Mhm.

00:08:48.545 --> 00:08:51.345
I'll find some time
to have lunch with you tomorrow.

00:08:52.305 --> 00:08:53.505
I'll wait for you.

00:08:54.025 --> 00:08:55.465
I'm heading home now.

00:08:58.665 --> 00:09:01.065
Don't you want to come inside and relax?

00:09:01.145 --> 00:09:03.025
Let's do it another day.

00:09:06.425 --> 00:09:10.825
Are you still upset about that day?

00:09:11.545 --> 00:09:16.905
Not that much. But let's take it slow.

00:09:20.825 --> 00:09:22.185
Okay.

00:09:22.265 --> 00:09:25.585
Then drive home safely.

00:09:53.385 --> 00:09:56.825
Oh? Did you forget something?

00:10:01.705 --> 00:10:03.385
I've changed my mind.

00:10:07.865 --> 00:10:11.745
Then… do you want to stay the night?

00:10:17.065 --> 00:10:18.145
My house is pretty messy.

00:10:19.105 --> 00:10:21.585
No, it just looks lived-in.

00:10:22.105 --> 00:10:23.625
And there's a baby too.

00:10:24.265 --> 00:10:28.145
Once Donut starts walking,
it'll probably get even messier.

00:10:28.225 --> 00:10:30.225
So it's just the three of you?

00:10:30.305 --> 00:10:35.625
Mhm. The three of us, Dad, Mom, and son.

00:10:36.545 --> 00:10:39.665
Ing! How was your first date?

00:10:39.745 --> 00:10:41.145
Satisfied?

00:10:45.185 --> 00:10:46.505
Sorry.

00:10:46.585 --> 00:10:48.105
Too late now.

00:10:49.425 --> 00:10:51.065
Now that you've got company,

00:10:52.025 --> 00:10:54.265
I'll go hang out with my friends too.

00:10:55.305 --> 00:10:57.545
Ugh, don't stay out too late.

00:10:57.625 --> 00:10:58.785
Then it'll be early tomorrow.

00:11:00.305 --> 00:11:01.465
Watch it.

00:11:02.065 --> 00:11:03.825
-I'm out. I'll go get changed now.
-Go.

00:11:03.905 --> 00:11:05.345
Please excuse me, Ms. Lin.

00:11:06.225 --> 00:11:07.225
Go, go.

00:11:08.065 --> 00:11:09.305
Oh, oh.

00:11:10.465 --> 00:11:13.465
Donut is asleep,
so don't worry about making noise.

00:11:14.065 --> 00:11:17.425
Making what noise? What's with you, Ith?

00:11:19.465 --> 00:11:20.425
Ugh.

00:11:22.665 --> 00:11:26.225
I'm sorry. He likes to joke like that.

00:11:29.825 --> 00:11:31.665
Let's take a shower, okay?

00:11:33.065 --> 00:11:37.345
I mean, I'll go take a shower.

00:11:43.545 --> 00:11:44.425
Come on.

00:11:54.665 --> 00:11:56.465
How are we supposed to sleep?

00:11:58.665 --> 00:12:00.465
Do we sleep on the same bed?

00:12:02.145 --> 00:12:03.705
I wouldn't get to sleep, would I?

00:12:03.785 --> 00:12:04.785
IngIng.

00:12:05.745 --> 00:12:06.905
Yes?

00:12:07.505 --> 00:12:08.705
You're out of liquid soap.

00:12:09.305 --> 00:12:10.625
Oh, right.

00:12:15.865 --> 00:12:17.945
I bought a refill. Wait a minute.

00:12:21.345 --> 00:12:24.505
Ms. Lin,
I'll put it down here by the door.

00:12:24.585 --> 00:12:26.465
You can come in and give it to me.

00:12:26.545 --> 00:12:27.705
Huh?

00:12:29.425 --> 00:12:32.385
I can't, Ms. Lin. You're naked.

00:12:36.745 --> 00:12:38.385
I'll hand it to you.

00:12:40.705 --> 00:12:43.465
Here. Please refill it.

00:12:44.105 --> 00:12:45.105
Thank you.

00:12:46.425 --> 00:12:47.865
I can't grab it.

00:12:52.705 --> 00:12:54.345
Still can't grab it.

00:12:54.425 --> 00:12:55.785
Wait a sec.

00:12:56.625 --> 00:12:57.745
Can you grab it now?

00:13:18.225 --> 00:13:19.545
Wanna take a shower together?

00:13:36.105 --> 00:13:37.145
Yes, Jane?

00:13:37.225 --> 00:13:39.065
Where are you, Ms. Lin?

00:13:39.705 --> 00:13:40.585
What is it?

00:13:41.105 --> 00:13:43.705
I'm at your house with the documents,
but you're not here.

00:13:43.785 --> 00:13:46.185
Leave them there.
I'll sign them when I get back.

00:13:46.265 --> 00:13:47.985
Are you still at the restaurant?

00:13:49.585 --> 00:13:51.065
Who are you with?

00:13:51.145 --> 00:13:52.505
I've got to go now.

00:13:53.665 --> 00:13:54.985
Oh?

00:14:18.785 --> 00:14:21.625
Is she going to think I dress too sexy?

00:14:22.705 --> 00:14:24.545
Will it tease her too much?

00:15:05.585 --> 00:15:08.305
Ms. Lin. Ms. Lin.

00:15:14.465 --> 00:15:15.545
I'm ready.

00:15:19.585 --> 00:15:22.865
I mean, I'm ready to go to bed.

00:15:22.945 --> 00:15:24.745
I'm still not sleepy.

00:15:27.185 --> 00:15:28.705
What should we do?

00:15:35.185 --> 00:15:36.465
I've got an idea.

00:15:43.585 --> 00:15:44.785
Do you want to go to sleep?

00:15:45.385 --> 00:15:47.665
Nah, I'm not sleepy.

00:15:49.825 --> 00:15:51.345
I'm having fun.

00:16:06.345 --> 00:16:07.505
I'm out of cards to play.

00:16:09.545 --> 00:16:12.185
Then you lose.

00:16:14.985 --> 00:16:16.345
Yay, I won.

00:16:18.345 --> 00:16:20.345
-Let's go to sleep.
-No.

00:16:23.065 --> 00:16:25.225
-Time to go.
-I'll just sleep here.

00:16:55.065 --> 00:16:56.905
When did I pass out?

00:16:59.865 --> 00:17:01.425
Why don't I remember anything?

00:17:30.065 --> 00:17:31.025
Morning kiss.

00:17:31.665 --> 00:17:32.505
Morning.

00:17:34.985 --> 00:17:37.105
How did I get into the bedroom last night?

00:17:37.825 --> 00:17:39.225
Do you know how light you are?

00:17:39.305 --> 00:17:40.305
Huh?

00:17:42.665 --> 00:17:45.025
So where did you sleep?

00:17:51.625 --> 00:17:52.785
Aren't you sore?

00:17:54.025 --> 00:17:57.105
I doze off on the couch at home
until morning all the time.

00:18:04.265 --> 00:18:07.665
Why do these look so good?
Did you make them yourself?

00:18:07.745 --> 00:18:08.865
I ordered them.

00:18:10.105 --> 00:18:12.945
I knew it. You don't look like you cook.

00:18:13.025 --> 00:18:17.425
How could you say that? You have no idea.
I'd pass on savory,

00:18:17.505 --> 00:18:19.825
but my desserts are Michelin-star quality.

00:18:21.185 --> 00:18:23.785
Michelin-star? Are you bragging?

00:18:26.185 --> 00:18:28.865
I need to head home now,
or I'll be late for work.

00:18:30.985 --> 00:18:33.145
Gotta go. I'll text you later.

00:18:45.545 --> 00:18:48.145
Enough. Time to go. Hurry.

00:19:01.185 --> 00:19:02.185
Bye-bye.

00:19:13.505 --> 00:19:15.105
I'll text you later.

00:19:18.665 --> 00:19:19.785
What?

00:19:21.465 --> 00:19:24.945
Finally, my sister has fallen in love
like everyone else.

00:19:28.745 --> 00:19:30.825
-Ing.
-What?

00:19:30.905 --> 00:19:33.385
You've done so much for others.

00:19:34.945 --> 00:19:36.345
Make yourself happy for a change.

00:19:37.265 --> 00:19:41.265
This one has my support. I love this.

00:19:42.865 --> 00:19:43.705
So annoying.

00:19:48.745 --> 00:19:49.905
Ing.

00:19:50.705 --> 00:19:52.545
I'm truly happy for you.

00:19:52.625 --> 00:19:56.385
Yeah, just come eat.
Stop standing over there yapping.

00:20:04.825 --> 00:20:05.825
Where's the water?

00:20:17.025 --> 00:20:21.065
We're running a promotion right now.
Buy one pass and get another one for free.

00:20:21.145 --> 00:20:22.025
-Hello.
-Here.

00:20:22.625 --> 00:20:26.065
Hello. Hi. Here you go.

00:20:26.145 --> 00:20:27.705
Bye-bye.

00:20:27.785 --> 00:20:30.585
-New promotion. Buy one, get one free.
-Thank you.

00:20:30.665 --> 00:20:32.705
-Here you go.
-You want it?

00:20:39.185 --> 00:20:40.145
Are you hungry?

00:20:44.265 --> 00:20:45.625
Please hold these for me.

00:20:48.185 --> 00:20:49.425
Ugh.

00:20:55.945 --> 00:20:57.905
-Can you open it?
-Yes.

00:20:59.785 --> 00:21:00.945
Does it look good?

00:21:01.025 --> 00:21:03.505
Looks so good. Are you hungry?

00:21:03.585 --> 00:21:04.745
I'm starving.

00:21:05.305 --> 00:21:08.185
Whoa, this looks amazing!

00:21:10.025 --> 00:21:10.945
I spilled it.

00:21:13.225 --> 00:21:14.265
Is it good?

00:21:16.505 --> 00:21:20.265
And…

00:21:22.185 --> 00:21:24.065
Here, you try it first.

00:21:36.145 --> 00:21:38.305
Nom, nom.

00:21:40.185 --> 00:21:41.145
Good job.

00:22:11.345 --> 00:22:13.425
So handsome…

00:22:17.385 --> 00:22:18.585
No, I can't.

00:23:49.025 --> 00:23:52.145
You still haven't told me
anything about Donut.

00:23:53.065 --> 00:23:55.425
But if you're not
comfortable sharing, it's okay.

00:23:57.945 --> 00:23:59.025
I can tell you.

00:24:01.305 --> 00:24:05.545
It's been a long time. I've dealt with it.

00:24:08.345 --> 00:24:10.185
My mom and dad

00:24:11.025 --> 00:24:13.185
made me marry Donut's father

00:24:14.905 --> 00:24:18.065
because they didn't want me
to be with women.

00:24:18.785 --> 00:24:21.265
So your family knew.

00:24:23.065 --> 00:24:26.585
They knew, but they couldn't accept it.

00:24:29.465 --> 00:24:33.185
But you didn't need to give in, did you?
That's your whole life.

00:24:34.465 --> 00:24:38.625
Back then, my mom was unwell,

00:24:40.865 --> 00:24:43.105
and her condition was getting worse.

00:24:46.265 --> 00:24:50.865
When they used that to convince me,
I really didn't know what to say.

00:24:52.345 --> 00:24:56.745
But your love grew,
and you two had Donut together, right?

00:24:57.425 --> 00:24:58.825
Actually…

00:25:01.545 --> 00:25:03.985
we were married in name only.

00:25:04.785 --> 00:25:09.105
But… I refused to sleep with him,

00:25:10.665 --> 00:25:12.065
so we fought all the time.

00:25:17.985 --> 00:25:19.225
And that day…

00:25:23.265 --> 00:25:25.905
he drugged my water and made me drink it.

00:25:36.185 --> 00:25:37.625
You can stop now.

00:25:38.585 --> 00:25:41.345
I'm sorry. I shouldn't have asked.

00:25:47.865 --> 00:25:51.825
Don't cry. It's all in the past now.

00:25:52.665 --> 00:25:53.825
Forget it.

00:25:55.305 --> 00:25:57.665
Right now, you have me.

00:29:51.105 --> 00:29:55.065
Your boss has been busy lately?
I haven't seen her at all.

00:29:57.785 --> 00:30:01.025
And today is her day off.
Where did she go?

00:30:03.665 --> 00:30:05.025
She's headed to the amusement park.

00:30:05.625 --> 00:30:06.705
Why would she go there?

00:30:08.265 --> 00:30:12.625
Well, to see that same Play Park manager.

00:30:16.145 --> 00:30:18.105
From my observation,

00:30:18.185 --> 00:30:23.425
if I'm not mistaken,
I think Ms. Lin is in love, sir.

00:30:37.545 --> 00:30:41.545
Dad, I've found my baking instructor.

00:30:43.225 --> 00:30:44.905
Prae, this is my dad.

00:30:57.065 --> 00:31:00.465
Prae, please call me back.
I'm home all day today.

00:31:01.185 --> 00:31:05.505
You can call me anytime. I miss you.

00:31:08.145 --> 00:31:09.425
Did anything happen, dear?

00:31:09.505 --> 00:31:13.785
Prae texted me saying she'd like to quit.
She won't be coming back.

00:31:13.865 --> 00:31:14.985
Why?

00:31:15.665 --> 00:31:17.025
I have no idea.

00:31:17.905 --> 00:31:20.025
She didn't pick up my calls either.

00:31:29.025 --> 00:31:31.585
Lin, come eat with me.

00:31:31.665 --> 00:31:33.545
I'm not hungry, Dad.

00:31:34.185 --> 00:31:36.785
But you haven't eaten anything
since this morning.

00:31:36.865 --> 00:31:38.825
I just can't bring myself to eat.

00:31:40.945 --> 00:31:44.185
Haven't I told you that your goal

00:31:44.265 --> 00:31:46.665
is to study hard and get into university?

00:31:47.545 --> 00:31:50.985
Having hobbies isn't necessary right now.

00:31:51.065 --> 00:31:54.945
I shouldn't have let you
take those stupid pastry classes.

00:31:55.025 --> 00:31:59.065
It was a waste of time and it distracted
you. You gained nothing from it.

00:32:33.785 --> 00:32:38.345
-Then we'll add this first. And crush it.
-Uh-huh.

00:32:38.425 --> 00:32:40.505
-Crush it? And then this?
-Make it dense.

00:32:40.585 --> 00:32:42.385
-Yes.
-Okay.

00:32:42.465 --> 00:32:44.385
We'll make the base layer first.

00:32:44.465 --> 00:32:48.065
-Here. Then add that in.
-Is the base good?

00:32:48.145 --> 00:32:50.585
Oh, no. Not yet. Squeeze this in first.

00:32:50.665 --> 00:32:51.665
The cream.

00:33:23.425 --> 00:33:26.385
Okay. And this is the final touch.

00:33:26.465 --> 00:33:27.785
Just put it on top.

00:33:28.345 --> 00:33:31.185
-Three of them?
-Three. Want another one?

00:33:31.265 --> 00:33:34.625
One more. Yay.

00:33:35.425 --> 00:33:37.905
-It's all done.
-Looks so good!

00:33:38.745 --> 00:33:39.585
Can I eat it now?

00:33:39.665 --> 00:33:42.345
Wait. Refrigerate it so it can set.
It'll taste better.

00:33:42.425 --> 00:33:43.425
-Oh, really?
-Mhm.

00:33:43.505 --> 00:33:45.545
-Want to try making another one?
-Mhm.

00:34:34.985 --> 00:34:38.025
It's done. Does it look good?

00:34:39.225 --> 00:34:40.585
Is something wrong?

00:34:40.665 --> 00:34:42.344
Nothing. I'm okay.

00:34:43.465 --> 00:34:45.385
Then why aren't you smiling at all?

00:34:46.905 --> 00:34:48.105
Smile for me.

00:34:52.105 --> 00:34:54.585
Is it good? I did a great job, didn't I?

00:34:54.665 --> 00:34:57.545
Next time, let's make macarons.

00:34:58.185 --> 00:35:01.305
I'm in. But isn't it hard?

00:35:01.385 --> 00:35:03.545
It's not that hard. I'll teach you.

00:35:04.985 --> 00:35:05.825
Okay.

00:35:07.745 --> 00:35:09.505
Come on. Let's put the lids on.

00:35:13.265 --> 00:35:14.785
Put on the lid.

00:35:16.065 --> 00:35:17.065
And this one.

00:35:27.745 --> 00:35:29.185
Look so delicious.

00:35:29.945 --> 00:35:31.585
The desserts, or someone here?

00:35:31.665 --> 00:35:33.225
You don't even need to ask.

00:35:35.825 --> 00:35:37.905
-Let's try it.
-Mhm.

00:35:48.065 --> 00:35:48.945
How is it?

00:35:52.265 --> 00:35:53.545
So sweet,

00:35:54.265 --> 00:35:55.625
but delicious.

00:35:56.705 --> 00:35:59.625
-It's delicious.
-Then eat it all.

00:36:02.145 --> 00:36:04.305
Where did you learn
to make these desserts?

00:36:05.065 --> 00:36:08.025
Well, I know the basics.
I've taken some classes.

00:36:08.105 --> 00:36:09.945
And then I watched tutorials on YouTube.

00:36:12.025 --> 00:36:13.945
So you make them
for your dad every day, right?

00:36:15.545 --> 00:36:18.985
-I never make any for him.
-Oh? Why not?

00:36:19.065 --> 00:36:22.825
Dad didn't want me making desserts.
He said it distracted me from my studies.

00:36:22.905 --> 00:36:25.185
I'd make some behind his back
once in a while.

00:36:26.945 --> 00:36:31.145
But when you make desserts,
you look so happy.

00:36:32.225 --> 00:36:35.825
It's fun, and I feel relaxed
every time I make them.

00:36:39.345 --> 00:36:42.945
Then, for Play Park's farewell party,

00:36:43.025 --> 00:36:44.745
do you want to make desserts for the kids?

00:36:44.825 --> 00:36:46.185
Would that be a good idea?

00:36:46.265 --> 00:36:50.505
Of course. If they taste this good,
the kids will love them.

00:36:50.585 --> 00:36:53.505
Then you have to finish it first
before I say yes.

00:36:54.225 --> 00:36:55.305
Okay.

00:37:01.905 --> 00:37:04.385
-You're crazy!
-Come on.

00:37:04.465 --> 00:37:05.665
‎No.

00:37:23.425 --> 00:37:25.425
FAREWELL PLAY PARK

00:37:25.505 --> 00:37:29.905
Guys, for Play Park's farewell party,
I think we shouldn't build a new stage.

00:37:29.985 --> 00:37:33.985
We'll use the stage we already have,
but add new activity zones.

00:37:34.065 --> 00:37:36.265
So there will be booths
for activities and games,

00:37:36.345 --> 00:37:38.825
like balloon dart, can toss,

00:37:38.905 --> 00:37:41.745
ring toss, and a shooting gallery.
Kids love those games.

00:37:41.825 --> 00:37:43.905
And I think there should be food.

00:37:43.985 --> 00:37:48.185
Basically, one savory dish
and one dessert. Sound good?

00:37:48.265 --> 00:37:49.865
-Yes.
-Yes.

00:37:50.505 --> 00:37:54.185
Let's help each other.
I'm putting my heart and soul into this.

00:37:55.105 --> 00:37:55.985
Anything you want to do?

00:37:56.065 --> 00:37:58.265
I'll serve the desserts.

00:37:58.345 --> 00:38:01.225
Alright. Thank you so much.
What about you?

00:38:01.305 --> 00:38:03.265
I'll oversee the activity booths.

00:38:03.345 --> 00:38:04.745
Okay.

00:38:05.865 --> 00:38:08.625
There's not much time left
before the party. Give it your all.

00:38:12.385 --> 00:38:15.785
PLAY PARK
FOOD - GIFTS

00:38:38.865 --> 00:38:39.705
What are you doing?

00:38:42.305 --> 00:38:43.905
Here's your coffee, ma'am.

00:38:46.425 --> 00:38:48.265
Are you craving some ice cream?

00:38:48.345 --> 00:38:51.785
I happened to see it open on your monitor.

00:38:51.865 --> 00:38:55.065
Oh, I want to practice making it
for Play Park's farewell party.

00:38:55.145 --> 00:38:56.345
Oh, right.

00:38:56.425 --> 00:38:57.865
It's pretty hard.

00:39:02.745 --> 00:39:04.225
INGING

00:39:06.345 --> 00:39:07.465
Yes?

00:39:12.585 --> 00:39:13.785
I'm not busy.

00:39:15.305 --> 00:39:16.785
I'll see you.

00:39:22.905 --> 00:39:24.665
-What is it?
-Leave.

00:39:25.385 --> 00:39:27.265
Oh, leave. Yes, ma'am.

00:39:44.545 --> 00:39:47.905
Look. This cafe just opened recently.
Let's have some dessert.

00:39:47.985 --> 00:39:49.025
Let's go.

00:39:49.985 --> 00:39:50.945
I'll get the door.

00:39:56.985 --> 00:39:58.705
The cakes look so good.

00:39:59.465 --> 00:40:01.985
How are they this cute?

00:40:05.345 --> 00:40:08.665
This one looks delicious. This one too.

00:40:08.745 --> 00:40:10.305
And this one too.

00:40:10.385 --> 00:40:12.505
You want to eat all of that?

00:40:13.345 --> 00:40:14.705
You'll get chubby.

00:40:17.505 --> 00:40:18.785
What would you like to order?

00:40:19.825 --> 00:40:21.985
Please give us a moment to decide.

00:40:26.065 --> 00:40:27.025
Prae?

00:40:31.425 --> 00:40:32.265
Lin.

00:40:52.665 --> 00:40:55.185
You can't run away
from me again like this, Prae.

00:41:02.145 --> 00:41:04.025
I want to know the reason.

00:41:05.145 --> 00:41:07.065
What did I do to upset you?

00:41:07.945 --> 00:41:10.105
Why did you suddenly quit?

00:41:10.185 --> 00:41:12.745
And why did you just disappear
and not answer my calls?

00:41:13.385 --> 00:41:15.145
Your father asked me to quit.

00:41:25.025 --> 00:41:26.905
He saw what happened in the kitchen.

00:42:40.345 --> 00:42:42.185
He was really upset.

00:42:42.265 --> 00:42:46.065
He didn't take it well at all.
So he gave me a lump sum as capital

00:42:47.025 --> 00:42:49.425
and told me not to contact you again.

00:42:52.945 --> 00:42:55.345
That money helped pay for my school
until I graduated.

00:42:55.425 --> 00:42:58.345
You should've found a way to tell me.

00:42:58.425 --> 00:43:00.545
I thought I'd done something wrong.

00:43:03.345 --> 00:43:06.185
It still haunts me to this day.

00:43:17.905 --> 00:43:19.385
I'm sorry, Lin.

00:43:21.465 --> 00:43:23.105
For everything.

00:43:24.985 --> 00:43:26.505
Especially for how I…

00:43:26.585 --> 00:43:30.225
You don't need to apologize. I started it.

00:43:31.025 --> 00:43:33.345
You showed me what my heart really wants.

00:43:34.025 --> 00:43:36.425
I should thank you, really.

00:43:47.105 --> 00:43:50.585
I'm sorry, Lin. For everything.

00:43:53.905 --> 00:43:56.425
I never thought this day would come.

00:43:56.505 --> 00:44:00.065
I'd like to express my gratitude
to all Play Park customers.

00:44:02.785 --> 00:44:03.945
Thai traditional dress.

00:44:04.025 --> 00:44:05.865
A gun! A gun!

00:44:06.625 --> 00:44:08.745
Are you the manager?
Get me somewhere to hide.

00:44:08.825 --> 00:44:10.225
Go ahead. Walk. Hurry.

00:46:14.185 --> 00:46:17.025
Subtitle translation by:
Anan Pratchayakul